overview: Sing your ABCs with Elmo and all your favorite Sesame Street Muppets! Float with an astronaut in space, juggle with a robot, and swing by the "G Club" to hear the different sounds it makes! Packed with lively and engaging melodies, Alphabet Songs fosters a rich understanding of letters and vocabulary by emphasizing sounds and connecting them with visuals to reinforce the learning.
title: Sesame Street: Alphabet Songs
